author: Screen Junkies
description:
Clock in cause it's time for the Honest Trailer for Severance! Our outties had never seen the show and decided to binge it all over a weekend where all we ate were waffles and booze, but that sounds like a problem for our innies, no? This show is good! Do you think we'll get some answers in season 3 for what the F it is we're watching?

If you're still reading this, comment "Are we having fun yet?" below
